Kerala Ayurveda Natural Remedies for Skin Care

{/* Introduction */}

Ayurveda, the ancient science of healing, focuses on balancing the three doshas (Vata, Pitta, and Kapha) to maintain healthy skin. Kerala Ayurveda emphasizes herbal remedies, oils, and natural treatments.

{/* Skincare Routine */}

Daily Ayurvedic Skin Care Routine

  • Cleansing: Use raw milk or rose water.
  • Exfoliation (Twice a Week): Besan, turmeric, and rose water.
  • Moisturizing: Coconut or almond oil.

üåô Night Routine

  • Face Massage: Apply Kumkumadi oil.
  • Toner: Use tulsi or saffron-infused water.
  • Lip Care: Apply ghee for hydration.
